Preconditions:
The input array "arr" must not be null.
The input array "arr" must not be empty.

Postconditions:
The method should return an integer value representing the maximum sum of a non-empty subarray with at most one element deletion.
The maximum sum should be calculated considering contiguous elements in the subarray.
The subarray should have at least one element remaining after the deletion (if any).
The sum of the remaining elements in the subarray should be the maximum possible.